{"tid":2428420,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人知點解逸東酒店個網底有條支那link?","createTime":"2021-03-01T14:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T14:29:18.000Z","uid":104721,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"43178adb3870a4ab73f524075c585819a1e08c88","tid":2428420,"uid":104721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaGJVJx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaGJVJx.png&h=817bf7cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖， 「<span class=\"red\">沪ICP备09039361号</span>」係link去&quot;www .beian .miit .gov .cn&quot;<br />\n上網查條link係「<span class=\"blue\">中華人民共和國工業和信息化部</span>」網站備案域名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後「<span class=\"red\">沪ICP备09039361号</span>」應該係個「備案號」：<br />\n<em>根據工信部要求：已通過備案的用戶，在網站開通時應在網站首頁底部放置正確的備案號，並鏈接到工信部網址： beian .miit .gov .cn ，供公眾查詢核對。 </em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁唔係支那網先要加咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">[size=2]如果old news咗屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/size=1]</span>"},{"pid":"96c2c35ee97fd3364d606c0131aae2e3de1cac0c","tid":2428420,"uid":104721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"補酒店link <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eatonworkshop.com/zh-hant/hotel/hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eatonworkshop.com%2Fzh-hant%2Fhotel%2Fhong-kong&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1wy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=aac3d03b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eatonworkshop.com/zh-hant/hotel/hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"40b537b831abab4248ccd10f806a4c85153b3d87","tid":2428420,"uid":6003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:11:50.000Z","msg":"search「沪ICP备09039361号」會見到朗廷系嘅網都有呢個code<br />\n逸東同朗廷好似有啲關係架嘛"},{"pid":"00a05214876a4439d04e05d0aba569cd1a07b95b","tid":2428420,"uid":30836,"like":1,"disl